        Building Approvals in Queensland: What Sellers Need to Know Before Listing
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Unapproved building works can complicate a sale, but the situation is usually manageable if you identify and address it before going to market.
      </p>
